3).Using sorted() function, sort the list in ascending order.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
a=[3,34,5,6,7,74,34,2,2]
sorting=sorted(a)
print(sorting)
[2, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 34, 34, 74]
a
a=[3,34,5,6,7,74,34,2,2]
a.sort()
print(a)
[2, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 34, 34, 74]

